 * *

I am neither a missionary nor a mercenary. I do not sell anything to =
anyone, nor do I force anything on anyone. I just freely share what I know,=
 what I saw and what I am inspired to share. The rest is not in my hands.

=
I want to respectfully, humbly and lovingly invite those who have even an i=
ota of interest to check out the homam website! If one gets into the habit =
of performing homam regularly, it has the great potential to transform one'=
s life, materially and spiritually..

